description: Product description Start your engines and race into fun with the abeec 12 Pull Back Cars set – the ultimate collection of mini race cars designed for thrilling speed, creative play, and perfect party gifting. This vibrant 12-pack includes six assorted colours (two of each), offering plenty of variety for group activities, games, or party bag fillers. Each car is crafted from durable, child-safe plastic and features a smooth pull-back-and-go mechanism. Just pull them back and watch them zoom across floors and tables — no batteries or fuss required. Designed with compact proportions (approx. 4.5cm long), these vehicles fit perfectly in small hands and party favour bags. Whether you're organising a birthday party, school celebration, or simply looking to reward classroom achievement, these cars deliver maximum excitement in a mini size. Their colourful designs make them visually appealing, while their simplicity encourages imaginative, hands-on play. Great for both boys and girls aged 3 and above. From party games and prizes to stocking fillers and treasure hunts, the abeec pull back cars are a versatile toy set that brings joy to every occasion. Ready, set, race! Safety Warning Not suitable for children under 3
